{"id":"342229139_Z_4_Z_4_u-ADDITIVE_CYCLIC_AND_CONSTACYCLIC_CODES","abstract":"We study mixed alphabet cyclic and constacyclic codes over the two alphabets Z4, the ring of integers modulo 4, and its quadratic extension Z4[u]=Z4+uZ4,u2=0. Their generator polynomials and minimal spanning sets are obtained. Further, under new Gray maps, we find cyclic, quasi-cyclic codes over Z4 as the Gray images of both λ-constacyclic and skew λ-constacyclic codes over Z4[u]. Moreover, it is proved that the Gray images of Z4Z4[u]-additive constacyclic and skew Z4Z4[u]-additive constacyclic codes are generalized quasi-cyclic codes over Z4. Finally, several new quaternary linear codes are obtained from these cyclic and constacyclic codes.","authors":["Habibul Islam","Om Prakash","Patrick Solé"],"meta":["July 2020Advances in Mathematics of Communications","DOI:10.3934/amc.2020094","Projects: Quantum codes from cyclic, constacyclic codes over finite non-chain ringsAdditive cyclic and constacyclic codes"],"references":["335352401_Z_p_Z_p_s_mathbb_Z_pmathbb_Z_ps_-additive_cyclic_codes_are_asymptotically_good","330180412_SKEW_CYCLIC_CODES_OVER_F_4_R","329332239_On_ZpZpk-additive_codes_and_their_duality","308603176_24-additive_cyclic_codes","287567569_On_cyclic_codes_over_Zopf4_uZopf4_and_their_Zopf4-images","278114792_-Additive_Cyclic_Codes","275617426_The_Structure_of_Z2Z2s-Additive_Codes_Bounds_on_the_Minimum_Distance","271942872_On_Z_p_r_Z_p_s_-additive_codes","271665682_On_Z_2_Z_2_u_-additive_codes","267478982_Z_2_Z_4_-linear_codes_rank_and_kernel","265024268_Skew_Constacyclic_Codes_over_Galois_Rings","263238072_Z2Z4-additive_cyclic_codes_generator_polynomials_and_dual_codes","257554670_Z2Z4_-linear_codes_Generator_matrices_and_duality","257554406_Z2Z4-linear_codes_Rank_and_kernel","352804911_On_mathbb_Z_2mathbb_Z_4xi_-skew_cyclic_codes","339607144_Asymptotically_good_Z_p_r_Z_p_s_-additive_cyclic_codes","320766974_On_the_structure_of_Z_2_Z_2_u_3_-linear_and_cyclic_codes","320210186_A_cl